http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Delhi/BJP-MP-takes-to-%E2%80%98gandhigiri%E2%80%99-offers-roses-to-litterbugs/article13977529.ece

Litterbugs in Connaught Place were offered roses by New Delhi MP Meenakshi Lekhi, who took to ‘ gandhigiri’ on Saturday to promote the Swachh Bharat Mission.Attempting to bring a change in mindsets, the BJP MP requested Delhiites to participate in the government’s programme of keeping India clean. On Friday, Ms. Lekhi had launched a cleanliness and sanitation drive that will continue till January 26. She also administered a Swachh Bharat oath to visitors while promising to work actively for the cause.Accompanied by New Delhi Municipal Council officials, Ms. Lekhi suggested that people caught littering must be fined.